column3: Debut for umpires Jim Knauss, Randy Harvey and Mark Arata, who worked because the staff umpires were not working due to contract negotiations which stalled during spring training; the contract was settled but the assigned umpires could not get to Detroit in time to work the game; former AL umpire Bill deegan worked at HPFILENAME_TX"
